
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 05 of Elbow MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Capsule' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Capsule rupture' radio button is enabled
And 'Plica syndrome' radio button is enabled
And 'Arthritis' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Capsule rupture' radio button
Then 'Extraarticular joint effusion' auto checkbox is enabled and checked by default
